</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-89_ pf-r pf-c-lm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fXEqDS hwCMhq pf-90_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-ctqQKy eJZCTA pf-91_ pf-heading-1-h3">Recommendations
</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-cbTzjv cdRhtw pf-93_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hjGZqJ gtgMXo pf-94_ pf-text-1">Educate employees and individuals on the importance of eye safety and first aid awareness through regular training sessions and informational campaigns.


</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hjGZqJ gtgMXo pf-96_ pf-text-1">Ensure workplaces are equipped with appropriate first aid kits containing eye wash solutions, sterile dressings, and eye patches.



